C  EXPONENTIAL DISTRIBUTION   PCL(X) = EXP(-X/A)		C  EXPONENTIAL DISTRIBUTION   PCL(X) = EXP(-X/A)
C  THIS FUNCTION IS CALLED FORM HMESON, ISOBAR, AND VHMESO	C  THIS FUNCTION IS CALLED FORM HMESON, ISOBAR, AND VHMESO
C  ARGUMENTS:							C  ARGUMENTS:
C   A      = MEAN VALUE OF DISTRIBUTION				C   A      = MEAN VALUE OF DISTRIBUTION
C   B      = CUT FOR LIMITING MOMENTUM				C   B      = CUT FOR LIMITING MOMENTUM
C								C
